"title": "8112: certainty",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8112",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A sure knowledge or conviction that what is believed is true and trustworthy. Christian certainty does not arise from the credulity of the believer, but is based on the faithfulness and trustworthiness of God.</p>\n<h2>Affirmations and statements of certainty</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:25\">JOB 19:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh23:14\">JOS 23:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:3\">PSA 27:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:17\">DAN 3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:28\">MRK 5:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:21\">MAT 9:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:3-Luke1:4\">LUK 1:3–1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:38-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:38–8:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:8\">PHP 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:18-1John5:20\">1JN 5:18–5:20</a></p>\n<h2>Certainty in God</h2>\n<h3>Because of his character</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:18\">HEB 6:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num23:19-Num23:20\">NUM 23:19–23:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:9-Deut7:10\">DEU 7:9–7:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:3-Deut32:4\">DEU 32:3–32:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:28\">2SA 7:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:30-Ps18:31\">PSA 18:30–18:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:4\">ISA 26:4</a></p>\n<h3>Because his promises are confirmed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:16-Heb6:19\">HEB 6:16–6:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:8\">ROM 15:8</a></p>\n<h3>His intervention encourages certainty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:36-Judg6:40\">JDG 6:36–6:40</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:6-Exod16:8\">EXO 16:6–16:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:12-Exod33:23\">EXO 33:12–33:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh3:9-Josh3:13\">JOS 3:9–3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:36-1Kgs18:39\">1KI 18:36–18:39</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's certainty about his identity and mission</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:3\">JHN 13:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:31\">MRK 8:31</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:21\">MAT 16:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:22\">LUK 9:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:14-John10:18\">JHN 10:14–10:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:6-John14:11\">JHN 14:6–14:11</a></p>\n<h2>Certainty and the believer</h2>\n<h3>Certainty about who Jesus Christ is</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:12\">2TI 1:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:16\">MAT 16:16</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:29\">MRK 8:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:20\">LUK 9:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:27\">JHN 11:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:28-John20:29\">JHN 20:28–20:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:24\">JHN 21:24</a></p>\n<h3>Certainty of salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:21-2Cor1:22\">2CO 1:21–1:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:16\">ROM 4:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:31-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:31–8:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:6\">PHP 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:18-Heb6:19\">HEB 6:18–6:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:13\">1JN 4:13</a></p>\n<h3>Certainty gained through obedience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:3-1John2:6\">1JN 2:3–2:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:24-Matt7:27\">MAT 7:24–7:27</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:46-Luke6:49\">LUK 6:46–6:49</a></p>\n<h3>Certainty in prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:14-1John5:15\">1JN 5:14–5:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:7-Matt7:11\">MAT 7:7–7:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:9-Luke11:13\">LUK 11:9–11:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:19-Matt18:20\">MAT 18:19–18:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:21-Matt21:22\">MAT 21:21–21:22</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:22-Mark11:24\">MRK 11:22–11:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:13-John14:14\">JHN 14:13–14:14</a></p>\n<h3>An area of permissible uncertainty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:32-Mark13:37\">MRK 13:32–13:37</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:6-Acts1:7\">ACT 1:6–1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:1-1Thess5:2\">1TH 5:1–5:2</a></p>",
